com.sri.ai.grinder.api

Interface Registry

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Context
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CompleteMultiVariableContext, DefaultRegistry, MultiVariableContextWithCheckedProperty, TrueContext

    @Beta
public interface Registry
extends java.lang.Cloneable
    An object containing information about global symbols and their types, user-defined global objects, and a predicate for defining constants.
    Author:
    braz
